tourBios.prYrSeason: Made one cut in 2012, a tie for 26th at the ATB Financial Classic presented by TELUS, Re-gained non-exempt status with rounds of 74-71-74-77 at the 2012 Fall Q-School.

dyn.dynBios: Close friends with fellow PGA TOUR Canada member Michael Gligic. Student of Sean Foley and attended the Core Golf Academy in Florida for high school.
dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA TOUR Canada was T26th in 2012 at the ATB Financial Classic presented by TELUS.
